description:
Anthropic CEO Dario Amodei joins Axios co-founders Jim VandeHei and Mike Allen for a blunt conversation about what Congress should do as artificial intelligence accelerates faster than Washington is ready for.

Amodei lays out three specific actions lawmakers need to take and explains why waiting even a few years could lead to backlash, bad regulation, and serious national security risks.

He also warns that the biggest threat is not just job loss, but what happens when power, wealth, and trust concentrate faster than leaders are willing to admit.
